column5: Thanks everyone, shes pretty excited by the support, keep 'em going, you can rate it daily, thanks again!!  http://www.mycambrianford.com/node/79
I lost a family member this past summer who battled cancer until the end, so I voted for highlights for hope
Thank You.  Your support has encouraged me to work harder.   France.
Thank you for your support and I am so very sorry for your loss.  France.

I hope I win too!  Thank you for your support!  A Highlights for Hope car going around town will certainly bring attention to the cause.  We must make a difference!  Voting continues until the 22nd!  Then we will know!

A very good friend of mine, France, gives a ton of time to help cancer patients, she helps run a non profit organization called Highlights for Hope (you can check it out here) http://www.highlightsforhope.ca/  Anyway, they are trying to win a car from Cambrian Ford in Sudbury. If you would like to help out you can view the video and rate/vote for her here...  http://www.mycambrianford.com/node/79  France is a real go-getter and to be honest, I've never seen another individual work so hard to help others. Lets help her out. - its just a click away!  Even a superhero needs some help sometimes!
Done, and I just sent out a mass email. Recently lost a family member to this disease.  I just posted i to my Facebook account to try and get more. Great cause
good idea so I just did too. let's see some of OFC's "star power" support this too.
